PM Indiya don halartar barkewar haikali a wurin da aka yi jayayya
NEW DELHI (AP) - Firayim Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin baje koli a wata mai zuwa ga wani gidan ibada na Hindu a wani wurin da ake fama da rigingimu a arewacin Indiya inda 'yan addinin Hindu suka rushe wani masallaci na karni na 16 a shekarar 1992, a cewar amintaccen da ke kula da ginin haikalin.
An shirya bikin ne a ranar 5 ga watan Augusta, masu shirya kwanan wata sun ce taurari ne mai albarka ga Hindus, amma kuma hakan ya nuna shekara guda tun lokacin da majalisar dokokin Indiya ta kwace matsayinta na mafi yawan musulmi, Jammu da Kashmir.
Wannan alama ba za ta yiwu ba ga magoya baya da kuma abokan adawar jam'iyyar Bharatiya Janata ta Hindu ta Modi, ko kuma BJP, wacce ta yi shekaru da yawa ta hada da alkawarin da ta yi na rage cin gashin kan Kashmir da kuma gina haikali ga allahn Hindu Ram inda masallacin Mughal ya taɓa tsayawa, wani wurin da ke birnin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh wanda masu ibada suka yi imanin cewa shi ne wurin haihuwar Ram.
Saboda har yanzu cutar coronavirus na ci gaba da yaduwa a duk fadin Indiya, wacce ta ba da rahoton kashi na uku mafi girma a duniya, za a watsa bikin a gidan talabijin na jihohi kai tsaye kuma za a iyakance adadin mahalarta taron da masu kallo, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko kuma Kungiyar Hindu ta Duniya, wata kungiyar 'yan kishin Hindu da ke kawance da BJP.
