Sakataren Cikin Gida Priti Patel ya bukaci bayani daga Twitter da Instagram a kan 'abun ciki' Wiley tweets
Priti Patel ta bukaci bayani daga Twitter da Instagram a tsawon lokacin da aka dauka don cire sakonnin da Wiley ya yi.
A halin yanzu 'yan sanda suna bincike kan wasu kalamai na jayayya da aka wallafa a asusun mai zane-zane na Grime a kafofin watsa labarun.
Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida ya bayyana a ranar Lahadi cewa: "Sakamakon jayayya daga Wiley abin kunya ne."
"Bai kamata ba su samu damar ci gaba da kasancewa a Twitter da Instagram na tsawon lokaci ba kuma na nemi cikakken bayani a kansu."
"Dole ne kamfanonin kafofin watsa labarun su yi aiki da sauri don kawar da irin wannan kiyayya mai ban tsoro daga dandalin su."
An zargi Twitter da "karin jayayya" yayin da har yanzu ana ganin tweets na Wiley sa'o'i 12 bayan da aka fara sanya su.
Tun daga lokacin an cire wasu tweets kuma an sanyawa dan shekara 41-shekara dokar hana fita na tsawon kwanaki bakwai ta shafin.
A baya Twitter ya ce an kulle asusun Wiley na wani dan lokaci "saboda keta manufofinmu na nuna kyama", yayin da Facebook ya ce "babu wani wuri na kalaman nuna kyama a shafin Instagram."
'Yan sandan birni sun ce a ranar Asabar: "Ganawar tana daukar dukkan rahotannin jayayya da matukar muhimmanci, ana tantance abubuwan da suka dace."
A halin yanzu, kamfanin gudanarwa na Wiley, A-List Management, "ya yanke dukkanin dangantaka" da tauraron.
Tsohon manajan mai zane-zane a yanzu, John Woolf, wanda Yahudawa ne, ya rubuta a dandalin sada zumunta na Twitter cewa: "Bayan tweets na jayayya na Wiley a yau mu a @A_ListMGMT mun yanke dukkanin alaka da shi. Babu wani wuri a cikin al'umma don jayayya."
A baya ya ce bai goyi bayan ko kuma ya amince da abin da Wiley ya wallafa ba, amma zai yi magana da shi a asirce kuma "ta taimaka wajen ilmantar da shi."
Sai dai a wani bidiyo a shafin sada zumunta na Instagram, Wiley ya bayyana cewa shi ne ya yanke alaka da gudanarwarsa.
Sauran 'yan majalisar sun zargi Twitter saboda barin tweets su kasance a bayyane.
Kwamitin kwadago Jess Phillips ya ce a ranar Asabar:
"Kawai ga dukkanin kayan Wiley. Me ya sa a duniya @Twitter ta bar irin wannan tsattsauran ra'ayi na jayayya da ƙiyayya? Tana fuskantar dukkanin mummunan bugun jini, Yahudawa suna samun abubuwan da ba ku samu ba, suna da iko, suna tunanin cewa sun fi kyau... Wannan abu ne mai haɗari. Tabbas ya kamata ya sauka."
Dan majalisa Neil Coyle ya kara da cewa: "Gudanarwarsa na iya yin aiki da sauri fiye da @Twitter yana mai jaddada cewa, dokar (ciki har da Lissafin Harms na Yanar Gizo) ya kamata ta tabbatar da cewa ba a amfani da dandamali na kafofin watsa labarun don yada kiyayya ba."
John Mann, mashawarci mai zaman kansa na gwamnati a kan jayayya, ya ce tweets "ya nuna ainihin dalilin da ya sa doka ke bukatar canzawa don rike su zuwa lissafi mai kyau."
A halin yanzu, Gangamin Yaki da Cin Hanci ya bukaci 'yan sanda da su bincika abubuwan da Wiley ya yi, kuma ya yi kira ga a rufe asusunsa na kafofin watsa labarun "don hana ci gaba da zubar da dafin Yahudawa."
Wiley, wanda aka fi sani da Godfather of Grime wanda ainihin sunansa Richard Cowie, ya karbi MBE don ayyukan waƙa a 2018.
