Tun da farko a yau, ministan tsaro Rajnath Singh, karamin ministansa Shripad Naik, babban hafsan hafsoshin tsaro Janar Bipin Rawat, babban hafsan sojoji M Naravane, babban hafsan sojojin sama R K S Bhadauria da kuma babban hafsan sojojin ruwa Admiral Karambir Singh sun ba da gudummawa a Amar Jawan Jyoti a taron tunawa da yakin kasar.
