Ya yi nasara a kan Wisconsin a cikin Rose Bowl, inda ya yi gudu don uku touchdowns kuma aka kira shi MVP mai laifi.
Herbert zai fafata da tsohon soja Tyrod Taylor domin fara aiki.
Masu caji za su sami sabon kwata-kwata bayan da Philip Rivers ya tashi ta hanyar kamfanin dillancin labarai na kyauta bayan kakar wasanni 14 a matsayin farawa.
Murray shi ne na 23 a gaba daya bayan da Los Angeles ta yi ciniki da New England domin komawa zagayen farko.
